1. *Ugao* sobe je veoma mali. (The *corner* of the room is very small.)
2. Stojim u *uglu* ulice i razmišljam. (I am standing on the *corner* of the street and thinking.)
3. *Uglom* oka sam primetio kretanje. (I noticed the movement out of the *corner* of my eye.)
4. Stavila sam stolicu u *ugao* sobe. (I put a chair in the *corner* of the room.)
5. Život se dešava u mnogim *uglovima* sveta. (Life happens in many *corners* of the world.)
6. U *uglovima* knjige nalaze se važni podaci. (Important information can be found in the *margins* of the book.)
7. Naša zgrada ima *uglastu* fasadu. (Our building has an *angular* facade.)
8. Ulica je napravljena u obliku *ugaonog* trougla. (The street is shaped like a *triangular* angle.)
9. *Uglasti* predmeti su lako lomljivi. ( *Angular* objects are easily breakable.)
10. Umetnica je koristila *ugaone* oblike u svojim slikama. (The artist used *angular* shapes in her paintings.)